      "height": 260,
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "🎨 Frontend Stack\n\n• Next.js 14+ (App Router)\n• React 18+ (Server Components)\n• TypeScript 5+\n• TailwindCSS 3+\n• Redux/Zustand (State)\n• React Query (Data Fetching)\n• Chart.js (Visualization)\n• WebSocket/SSE (Real-time)",
