      "height": 260,
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "🚀 Backend Stack\n\n• Python 3.12+\n• FastAPI (REST + GraphQL)\n• Pydantic (Validation)\n• SQLAlchemy (ORM)\n• Alembic (Migrations)\n• Celery (Task Queue)\n• JWT (Authentication)\n• CORS, Rate Limiting",
