      "height": 260,
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "🧠 AI/ML Stack\n\n• LangGraph (Agent Framework)\n• LangChain (LLM Orchestration)\n• OpenAI GPT-4 (Language Model)\n• spaCy (NLP)\n• NumPy, Pandas (Data Processing)\n• Scikit-learn (ML)\n• Vector Embeddings\n• Prompt Engineering",
