      "height": 260,
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "💾 Data Stack\n\n• PostgreSQL 15+ (Primary DB)\n• Redis 7+ (Cache + Sessions)\n• GraphDB/RDF (Materials Graph)\n• SPARQL (Graph Queries)\n• Alembic (Migrations)\n• Backup: S3-compatible\n• Replication: Master-Slave\n• Connection Pooling",
