      "text": "🛠️ DevOps Stack\n\n• Docker + Docker Compose\n• GitHub Actions (CI/CD)\n• Nginx (Reverse Proxy)\n• Traefik (Load Balancer)\n• AWS/Azure (Cloud)\n• S3 (File Storage)\n• CloudWatch (Monitoring)\n• Sentry (Error Tracking)",
